{"id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0001", "text": "[Cyber attack](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberattack/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0001", "source_slug": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis", "source_title": "A cyber attack is a financial crisis", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis.html", "source_date": "2025-09-29", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 1, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0002", "text": "A cyber attack is not just an IT problem. It has direct consequences for the finances of your company. From small businesses to multinationals, everyone is at risk. An attack could lead to liquidity problems or even bankruptcy.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0002", "source_slug": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis", "source_title": "A cyber attack is a financial crisis", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis.html", "source_date": "2025-09-29", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0003", "text": "The direct costs of a cyber incident add up quickly. Think of IT research, legal assistance and crisis communication. Sometimes you also have to replace systems or pay a ransom. In addition, downtime causes loss of turnover. Customer orders are left behind, contracts are not fulfilled and fines may follow. Production and services often come to a standstill, which increases the damage.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0003", "source_slug": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis", "source_title": "A cyber attack is a financial crisis", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis.html", "source_date": "2025-09-29", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0004", "text": "A cyber attack also damages the company's reputation. Customers lose confidence and choose the competitor. New deals are not forthcoming, and you may need to offer discounts to win back customers. This reduces your profit margin. Investors are also reacting: share prices are falling and valuations for acquisitions are becoming lower.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0004", "source_slug": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis", "source_title": "A cyber attack is a financial crisis", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis.html", "source_date": "2025-09-29", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0005", "text": "Supervisors can impose fines for violations of privacy and cybersecurity rules. Business partners and customers can submit claims for damages. Legal proceedings and audits add to the financial pressure. Delivery problems within the chain cause additional costs and liability.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0005", "source_slug": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis", "source_title": "A cyber attack is a financial crisis", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis.html", "source_date": "2025-09-29", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0006", "text": "Cyber insurance does not always cover all costs. Premiums may increase after an event and crucial costs may be excluded from the policy. Entrepreneurs must therefore continue to invest in IT, security and compliance.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0006", "source_slug": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis", "source_title": "A cyber attack is a financial crisis", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis.html", "source_date": "2025-09-29", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0007", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig](https://www.samendigitaalveilig.nl/).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0007", "source_slug": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis", "source_title": "A cyber attack is a financial crisis", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis.html", "source_date": "2025-09-29", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0008", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0008", "source_slug": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis", "source_title": "A cyber attack is a financial crisis", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis.html", "source_date": "2025-09-29", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0009", "text": "- Do you have an SME company and do you want to reduce your cyber risks? Then take a look at [Cyber ​​Fundament](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-voor-het-mkb/), especially for SME entrepreneurs.\n- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) especially for large businesses and reduce your cyber risks.\n- Do you also want to [do business safely](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link)? View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars.\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis__c4-paragraph__0009", "source_slug": "een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis", "source_title": "A cyber attack is a financial crisis", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/een-cyberaanval-is-een-financiele-crisis.html", "source_date": "2025-09-29", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
